#: jsx/poolSpecimenForm.js:207
msgid "Pooling Note"
msgstr "样本合并说明"

#: jsx/poolSpecimenForm.js:208
msgid ""
"Select or Scan the specimens to be pooled. Specimens must\n"
"have a Status of 'Available', have a Quantity of greater\n"
"than 0, and share the same Type, PSCID, Visit Label\n"
"and Current Site. Pooled specimens cannot already belong "
"to a pool. Once pooled, the Status of specimen will be changed\n"
"to 'Dispensed' and there Quantity set to '0'"
msgstr ""
"选择或扫描要合并的样本。样本必须满足：\n"
"状态为“可用”、数量大于 0，且具有相同的类型、\n"
"PSCID、访视标签和当前站点。已合并的样本不能再次合并。\n"
"合并后，样本状态将更改为“已分发”，其数量将设为“0”。"

