#: jsx/specimenForm.js:189
msgid ""
"To create new aliquots, enter a Barcode, fill out the corresponding sub-form and press Submit.\n"
"Press the \"New Entry\" button to add another barcode field, or use the \"Copy\" button\n"
"to duplicate the previous entry."
msgstr ""
"要创建新的分装样本，请输入条形码，填写对应的子表单并按“提交”。\n"
"点击“新建条目”按钮添加另一个条形码字段，或使用“复制”按钮\n"
"以重复上一条目。"

#: jsx/specimenForm.js:199
msgid ""
"To create new specimens, first select a PSCID and Visit Label.\n"
"Then, enter a Barcode, fill out the corresponding sub-form and\n"
"press submit. Press \"New Entry\" button to add another barcode field, or\n"
"use the \"Copy\" button to duplicate the previous entry."
msgstr ""
"要创建新样本，请先选择 PSCID 和访视标签。\n"
"然后输入条形码，填写对应的子表单并按“提交”。\n"
"点击“新建条目”按钮添加另一个条形码字段，或使用“复制”按钮\n"
"以重复上一条目。"

